Supported tags and respective Dockerfile links
==============================================
6.1 ([docker-varnish/6.1/alpine3.8/Dockerfile](https://github.com/pockost/docker-varnish/blob/master/6.1/alpine3.8/Dockerfile))

Varnish image caching all standards asset.

Usage
======

```
docker run -d -e BACKEND_HOST=mybackend.internal pockost/varnish:6.1
```

Ports
=====
Port 6081 are exposed.

Environment variables
=====================

`BACKEND_HOST` Backend hostname or IP. Mandatory
`BACKEND_PORT` Backend port


Configuration
=============

If needed you can mount a config file inside `/etc/varnish/default.vcl`



